Benefits:
• {Cartographers}s receive priority map-testing for any creations. 
• {Cartographers}s gain access to Alchemy map-making tools.
• {Cartographers}s are often prioritized by Alchemy leadership for map script inclusion in guild-organized events.

Requirements:
• Be an Alchemy Affiliate.
• Maintain and occasionally add to the Alchemy Alliance map script online repository so that the rest of the community may enjoy their creativity. {Cartographer}s may take a break from scripting for as long as they need.
